<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_253_r1l12"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> brıef / vns von des handels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_r1l13"><expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd dem edeln <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu Heydek / vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_r1l14">mals vnd yecʒ geſandt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd ſeın vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_r1l15">ſölıch <expan>ʒweyu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> niht lıeb . Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_r1l16">des <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Heydek niht mechtıg ſeyn Vnd auch <expan>beſorg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_r1l17">Ob wır Jm von <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> erfarn <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
