<ab facs="#facs_253_r1l19"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade / vns des ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_line_1572960129050_571"><expan>verlaſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd in gut von vns <expan>aufcʒuneme<ex>n</ex></expan> . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_r1l22"><expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd <expan>wolgefalle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
